  "decision_conditions": [
    "<p>The proposed development would, by way of its siting, massing and design, result in the loss of the original butterfly roofline and the degradation of the original roofscape of the row of terraced properties, being an incongruous and unsympathetic addition to the subject site and the character of the row of terraces and the wider streetscene. The proposal is considered contrary to the NPPF, policy D4 (Delivering Good Design)of the London Plan 2021, policy LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character ) of Hackney’s Local Plan 2033 and Hackney’s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD.<br></p>"
